Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.93,0:02:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大兔  大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.78,0:02:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.15,0:02:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大兔？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.99,0:02:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对你...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.80,0:02:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大兔  我说大兔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.10,0:02:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  听我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:02:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该起来了  大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  HR早就结束了呀
